{
  "name": "RPlog_A_Second_Chance_with_Jal_Dana_Part_2",
  "title": "Furball at the Ord Mantell Line",
  "summary": "Along the Imperial-Republican border near Ord Mantell, the New Republic corvette Audacity and its Ghost Squadron of X-wings run a routine patrol while the hidden Imperial carrier Emancipator launches a TIE sweep led by Commander Wolf, shadowed by the inspecting Admiral Jal'Dana Rall in her stark-white interceptor and her wingman Boomer (Korolov). When Wolf engages prematurely, the two formations collide into a swirling dogfight in which the Corellian Captain Kesander 'Sandman' Beysarus, the X-wing ace Raxis 'Raptor' L'ygr in Ghost 3, and the Dug pilot Shovadu in Ghost 4 trade fire with the Imperials. Raxis recognizes the white TIE as Admiral Rall, and the corvette's controller Rasi orders the squadron to isolate and disable her fighter, turning the skirmish into a personal duel between the pilot she dubs 'Meat' and the Admiral. As the Star Destroyer Vindictive arrives and opens its lethal anti-fighter arcs, Jal'Dana orders all Imperial craft to regroup, and Kesander calls the Ghosts to break contact and limp home with light damage. Both sides count the engagement a draw with no losses, leaving the rivalry between Raxis and Admiral Rall unresolved.",
